snippet.title: Mystery of the Capsmith Demo RELEASE + DOWNLOAD! - SM64 ROM Hack
snippet.description:
The demo for Mystery of the Capsmith is here!  I made this game in 17 days for the Scuttle Hacking Competition and it won first place. This shorter competition/demo version doesn't have the story of the Capsmith, but the full version will. You guys can let me know what you think of it, and if you'd like to see it made into a larger hack or even a major hack.
This demo does not support N64 as its build doesn't have my newer optimizations.
Find the Cap Kingdom remix used in this trailer here: https://youtu.be/m6ZhmZa9mrQ

DOWNLOAD: https://romhacking.com/hack/Mystery-of-the-Capsmith-Demo
Like what you see? The best way to help out is if you want to spread the word and tell your friends about my mods!
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/dorrieal
SM64 ROM hack releases from me, both new and old: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLRzRbTL5z06lfgDRGWecznGPARS7t2RFi
I stream my game development live on Twitch: http://www.twitch.tv/dan_gptv

Subscribe to catch all releases and previews of every new adventure!
--
